Reasoning: The paper deals with image processing and document analysis, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with feature extraction and segmentation of text from documents. The use of compressed domain processing also involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Finally, the paper also involves multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with processing of different types of documents such as fax, invoices, and receipts.
